The new series of Doctor Who will arrive on screens in 2023

Read the full story
Gatwa is one of several Sex Education stars who will be appearing alongside Margot Robbie in Greta Gerwig’s much-hyped Barbie film, which is expected to hit cinemas in July 2023

The Independent’s Alexandra Pollard wrote of Gatwa’s character: “Eric, in particular, struck a chord when the show premiered – not just with those enamoured by his ebullience and killer wardrobe, but by people who had rarely, if ever, seen themselves on screen before.”

Gutwa's big break came in 2019 with Netflix’s hit teen show Sex Education. 

He told The Independent: “[The day it was released] I hopped onto a plane with 500 Instagram followers. Eight hours later, I hopped off the plane with a couple hundred thousand”

“People really cannot understand the concept of a black boy in a tracksuit in London being from Scotland. People think I’m taking the piss. I’m like, ‘Stop taking my Scottishness away. You don’t define me’”

“People have tried to fight me,” he told The Independent. “There’ve been times when I’ve been on a night out and people ask me where I’m from… The amount of times I’ve almost been beaten up for saying I’m Scottish. It’s given me an identity crisis”

“I was quite an easy target in a state Scottish high school. I grew up in a working-class area, and I stood out – for my voice, my appearance, I did dance and things like that. But I always had faith in my charm. I always had faith in my charisma”
In a 2020 interview, he told The Independent that his family were one of “like three black families in the whole of Edinburgh”
“They are someone that can help people escape, which I love”

“I feel like anyone can put themselves in those shoes. The Doctor is not from anywhere. They don’t fit in anywhere and I think for marginalised people they have been a real beacon of feeling seen in a way.
Speaking about diversity casting, Gatwa said of the Time Lord: “He is literally an alien – ‘they’ are an alien. And so they can regenerate into anything and anyone...
Gatwa will be the 14th actor and the first Black man to play the Doctor
He was discussing how actor Ncuti Gatwa had “dazzled” him in his audition to be the new Time Lord in Doctor Who
“Sometimes talent walks through the door and it’s so bright and bold and brilliant, I just stand back in awe and thank my lucky stars,” said Russell T Davies last weekend

Some Republicans, like Senator Josh Hawley, have lately begun attacking her for her past work as a public defender, focusing in particular on her work defending sexual offenders.

Jackson has been under consideration for a Supreme Court seat before. 

When Justice Scalia passed away unexpectedly in early 2016, she was one of five candidates whom then-president Barack Obama interviewed.

Jackson is appearing today before the Senate Judiciary Committee in the first of her confirmation hearings.

She seeks to not only become the first Black woman to sit on the nation’s highest court but also the first public defender.
